<h1>引入您最喜爱的语言</h1>
<div class="hero">
<h1>Windows Azure SDK</h1>
<div class="video" style="cursor: pointer; background-image: url('/../../../../../media/dev-video-other.png') !important;" onclick="document.location.href='http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=234530';">5 分 46 秒</div>
<div class="left-cont">
<h2>包括对任何语言的基础支持</h2>
<div class="dev-overview-install-btns">
<div class="install-btn-1"><a href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=254282&amp;clcid=0x409" class="windows"><span class="icon">下载</span> <span class="para">Windows Installer</span> </a><span>2012 年 6 月</span></div>
<div class="install-btn-2"><a href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=253471&amp;clcid=0x409" class="macintosh"><span class="icon">下载</span> <span class="para">Mac 安装程序</span> </a><span>2012 年 7 月</span></div>
<div class="install-btn-3"><a href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=253472" class="linux"><span class="icon">下载</span><span class="para">源代码</span> </a><span>azure-2012-07.tar.gz</span></div>
</div>
